==Korean==

===Verb suffix===

'''고요''' (go.yo)

{{korrom|rr=goyo|mr=koyo|yr=koyo}}

#  At the end of a question, to mark a shift from what has gone before.  Cf. English [[anyway]].
#  At the end of a statement, to mark an additional and complementary statement.  Cf. English [[as well]].

